$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (2, 31, 'Mojo Mobility partners with OEMs to design and develop unique, cutting-edge products that incorporate Mojos patented wireless charging technologies into a variety of different industries and applicationsfrom mobile devices, to industrial and medical devices, to electric vehicles.', 'Mojo Mobility partners with OEMs to design and develop unique, cutting-edge products that incorporate Mojos patented wireless charging technologies into a variety of different industries and applicationsfrom mobile devices, to industrial and medical devices, to electric vehicles.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (2, 32, '<p>\\r\\n	Established in 2005, Mojo Mobility has been at the forefront of the development of wireless power technologies that allow consumers to conveniently charge and power their devices. Mojo Mobility has partnered with a number of OEMs to create unique, advanced solutions for wireless charging for many different products. Mojo&rsquo;s unique proprietary Near Field Power<sup>&reg;</sup> technology allows position-free charging and powering of multiple devices simultaneously. Near Field Power<sup>&reg;</sup> places Mojo Mobility several generations ahead of their competitors by providing unsurpassed performance, cost, efficient power transfer and a simplified user experience.</p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n	Mojo has also partnered with OEMs to enhance the automotive experience in several ways. Mojo incorporates its wireless charging technology into various surfaces in the car, creating a safer and more convenient alternative to cord-charging. Mojo Mobility is also transforming the electric vehicle consumer experience by enabling high-power, efficient wireless charging of the vehicle. Mojo is eliminating the hassle of plug-in charging by enabling a user-friendly, ubiquitous method of charging electric vehicles wirelessly.&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n', 'Established in 2005, Mojo Mobility has been at the forefront of the development of wireless power technologies that allow consumers to conveniently charge and power their devices. Mojo Mobility has partnered with a number of OEMs to create unique, advanced solutions for wireless charging for many different products. Mojos unique proprietary Near Field Power technology allows position-free charging and powering of multiple devices simultaneously. Near Field Power places Mojo Mobility several generations ahead of their competitors by providing unsurpassed performance, cost, efficient power transfer and a simplified user experience. Mojo has also partnered with OEMs to enhance the automotive experience in several ways. Mojo incorporates its wireless charging technology into various surfaces in the car, creating a safer and more convenient alternative to cord-charging. Mojo Mobility is also transforming the electric vehicle consumer experience by enabling high-power, efficient wireless charging of the vehicle. Mojo is eliminating the hassle of plug-in charging by enabling a user-friendly, ubiquitous method of charging electric vehicles wirelessly.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 43, 'Position Freedom', 'Position Freedom');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 44, '<p>\\r\\n	Mojo Mobility&rsquo;s unique Near Field Power&reg; allows consumers to charge their devices position free by placing the device anywhere on the charging surface.</p>\\r\\n', 'Mojo Mobilitys unique Near Field Power allows consumers to charge their devices position free by placing the device anywhere on the charging surface.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 45, 'Multi-Device', 'Multi-Device');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 46, '<p>\\r\\n	Using a unique patented design, Mojo Mobility&rsquo;s charging solutions allow multiple devices with different power requirements to be charged simultaneously on the same charging surface.</p>\\r\\n', 'Using a unique patented design, Mojo Mobilitys charging solutions allow multiple devices with different power requirements to be charged simultaneously on the same charging surface.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 47, 'Integration', 'Integration');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 48, '<p>\\r\\n	Mojo&rsquo;s small receiver circuit allows for easy integration and high reliability into products such as mobile devices, cases, and batteries. Mojo Mobility&rsquo;s Near Field Power&reg; is compatible with popular wireless charging industry standards.</p>\\r\\n', 'Mojos small receiver circuit allows for easy integration and high reliability into products such as mobile devices, cases, and batteries. Mojo Mobilitys Near Field Power is compatible with popular wireless charging industry standards.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 49, 'Wireless vs. Cord-Charging', 'Wireless vs. Cord-Charging');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 50, '<p>\\r\\n	Mojo&rsquo;s wireless charging performance is comparable to conventional cord-charging in that it is fast, highly efficient, and able to meet charging power levels ranging from 1W to 90W and higher for mobile devices and up to 20kW for electric vehicles. Consumers will experience no charging performance degradation when switching to Mojo&rsquo;s wireless technology.</p>\\r\\n', 'Mojos wireless charging performance is comparable to conventional cord-charging in that it is fast, highly efficient, and able to meet charging power levels ranging from 1W to 90W and higher for mobile devices and up to 20kW for electric vehicles. Consumers will experience no charging performance degradation when switching to Mojos wireless technology.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 51, 'Safe Charging Technology', 'Safe Charging Technology');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 52, '<p>\\r\\n	Wireless charging technology provides many safety advantages over conventional cord charging. Mojo&#39;s unique Near Field Power&reg; system provides:</p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n	<li>\\r\\n		A safety advantage in waterproof or sealed environments due to the lack of connecting points that conventional cord-charging requires</li>\\r\\n	<li>\\r\\n		A charging surface that does not heat up metallic objects, making it a safe place to put coins and keys</li>\\r\\n	<li>\\r\\n		Electromagnetic emissions that conform to all regulatory guidelines</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n', 'Wireless charging technology provides many safety advantages over conventional cord charging. Mojo&#039;s unique Near Field Power system provides: A safety advantage in waterproof or sealed environments due to the lack of connecting points that conventional cord-charging requires A charging surface that does not heat up metallic objects, making it a safe place to put coins and keys Electromagnetic emissions that conform to all regulatory guidelines');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (35, 53, 'Mojos patented Near Field Power enables next generation wireless charging systems.', 'Mojos patented Near Field Power enables next generation wireless charging systems.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 54, 'Mojo Mobility partners with Original Equipment Manufactures (OEMs) to develop unique, differentiated solutions for wireless charging.', 'Mojo Mobility partners with Original Equipment Manufactures (OEMs) to develop unique, differentiated solutions for wireless charging.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 55, 'Mobile', 'Mobile');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 56, '<p>\\r\\n	Mojo Mobility&rsquo;s Near Field Power&reg; technology enables mobile device manufacturers to develop innovative products that are charged or powered wirelessly. By using Mojo&rsquo;s technology, mobile products such as mobile phones, laptops, tablets, and wireless accessories can be charged on one position-free wireless charging surface&mdash;drastically reducing the number of chargers manufacturers must produce and consumers carry with them.</p>\\r\\n', 'Mojo Mobilitys Near Field Power technology enables mobile device manufacturers to develop innovative products that are charged or powered wirelessly. By using Mojos technology, mobile products such as mobile phones, laptops, tablets, and wireless accessories can be charged on one position-free wireless charging surfacedrastically reducing the number of chargers manufacturers must produce and consumers carry with them.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 57, 'Wearable Technology', 'Wearable Technology');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 58, '<p>\\r\\n	Wearable electronics pose unique challenges to product designers due to the small volume, minimal weight, and rugged use environments. Mojo Mobility&rsquo;s Near Field Power&reg; technology provides a position free, waterproof, small volume wireless charging solution that allows product designers to develop advanced, unique products that are charged with no cords attached.</p>\\r\\n', 'Wearable electronics pose unique challenges to product designers due to the small volume, minimal weight, and rugged use environments. Mojo Mobilitys Near Field Power technology provides a position free, waterproof, small volume wireless charging solution that allows product designers to develop advanced, unique products that are charged with no cords attached.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 59, 'Automotive Infrastructure', 'Automotive Infrastructure');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 60, '<p>\\r\\n	Integration of Mojo&rsquo;s Near Field Power&reg; technology into the interior of a vehicle allows the occupant to free themselves of the cumbersome mobile device power cord while instantaneously allowing integrated communication with the on board information and entertainment system. The ability to charge multiple devices simultaneously at any location greatly enhances the consumer experience as well as safety within the vehicle.</p>\\r\\n', 'Integration of Mojos Near Field Power technology into the interior of a vehicle allows the occupant to free themselves of the cumbersome mobile device power cord while instantaneously allowing integrated communication with the on board information and entertainment system. The ability to charge multiple devices simultaneously at any location greatly enhances the consumer experience as well as safety within the vehicle.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 61, 'Electric Vehicle Charging', 'Electric Vehicle Charging');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 62, '<p>\\r\\n	Mojo&rsquo;s Near Field Power&reg; technology is truly scalable and wireless power up to 20kW can be achieved. By partnering with major automobile manufacturers and with the backing of the United States Department of Energy, Mojo Mobility is creating high power, highly efficient, and position free wireless charging systems that will transform the way we power and charge electric vehicles.</p>\\r\\n', 'Mojos Near Field Power technology is truly scalable and wireless power up to 20kW can be achieved. By partnering with major automobile manufacturers and with the backing of the United States Department of Energy, Mojo Mobility is creating high power, highly efficient, and position free wireless charging systems that will transform the way we power and charge electric vehicles.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 63, 'Consumer', 'Consumer');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 64, '<p>\\r\\n	Mojo Mobility&rsquo;s Near Field Power&reg; technology provides an intuitive, easy to use method for charging or powering multiple devices simultaneously in a position free manner. It allows the consumer to limit the number of charging cords and devices they must keep track of, thus simplifying their lives.</p>\\r\\n', 'Mojo Mobilitys Near Field Power technology provides an intuitive, easy to use method for charging or powering multiple devices simultaneously in a position free manner. It allows the consumer to limit the number of charging cords and devices they must keep track of, thus simplifying their lives.');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 65, 'Other Applications', 'Other Applications');";
$k_stmts[] = "INSERT INTO ".K_TBL_DATA_TEXT." (page_id, field_id, value, search_value) VALUES (36, 66, '<p>\\r\\n	Mojo Mobility&rsquo;s Near Field Power&reg; technology allows medical and industrial devices to benefit from the advantages of wireless charging. The waterproof sealed nature of Mojo&rsquo;s wireless power technology is ideal for the sterile environments of the medical industry and the harsh environments of industrial application. These vital industries are also able to charge multiple devices simultaneously and efficiently. Most importantly, the lack of cords allow for a simplified charging system.</p>\\r\\n', 'Mojo Mobilitys Near Field Power technology allows medical and industrial devices to benefit from the advantages of wireless charging. The waterproof sealed nature of Mojos wireless power technology is ideal for the sterile environments of the medical industry and the harsh environments of industrial application. These vital industries are also able to charge multiple devices simultaneously and efficiently. Most importantly, the lack of cords allow for a simplified charging system.');";
